    {
        "content": "<p>Regarding SICM, my personal interest favors project <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/2\">#2</a> over project <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/1\">#1</a>, i.e. reproducing SICM in Lean for pedagogical purposes rather than formalization.  However regarding formalization, I've made significant progress on one approach to special relativity which you can see here if so inclined: <a href=\"https://github.com/mettinger/Relativity\">https://github.com/mettinger/Relativity</a>.</p>",
        "id": 565601121,
        "sender_full_name": "Mark Ettinger",
        "timestamp": 1766965662
    },
